you know, into some analytic field. And at the time, data science was a thing, but there weren't

00:37:27.113 --> 00:37:36.073
really that many programs. So this was like 2015 or so. And UCSF had a master's in clinical

00:37:36.073 --> 00:37:40.953
research in Berkeley, was like talking about a data science program. And I was in the Bay Area,

00:37:41.592 --> 00:37:44.393
same reason everybody goes there for, you know, I was going to work at a startup and,

00:37:45.033 --> 00:37:53.433
you know, go public and get rich. Didn't, never worked. But the, the thing is, you know, it was,

