in the syntax. This is kind of the nature of open source tooling that these things evolve and

00:44:48.393 --> 00:44:58.473
change over time. And so stability, base R is more your friend than you realize. I think people

00:44:58.473 --> 00:45:04.953
underestimate how important base R is to doing a lot of, I would say just regular programming.

00:45:04.953 --> 00:45:10.393
