supervising or working with it. But the more that you go out on that edge of this is

00:45:21.432 --> 00:45:25.033
under development, under active development, the further that you're going to push the boundary

00:45:25.033 --> 00:45:31.192
that it comes at a cost of probably additional maintenance. And I think that maintenance is

